    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly exceptional specimen that can only be described as a time capsule. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, ensuring every inch remains in showroom condition. The exterior paint retains its deep, original luster, completely free of swirl marks, rock chips, or door dings, and has been treated with a multi-layer ceramic coating for long-term protection. Inside, the cabin is immaculate; the premium leather remains supple and matte, showing zero bolster wear, while the carpets have been protected by factory mats since day one. All interior electronics, switches, and displays function with tactile precision. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, featuring a fully documented service history performed exclusively by marque specialists. The engine bay is detailed to a concours standard, and the undercarriage is remarkably clean, reflecting its history as a fair-weather-only vehicle. This is a smoke-free, pet-free, and accident-free example that represents the pinnacle of its model year. Includes all original keys, manuals, and a custom car cover.",
